title: October early skin sales delayed?
body: I have RP saved to buy moo cow Alistar and it didn't even go on sale this month like they said it would. Is it because its included in a new bundle?{{sticker:zombie-brand-mindblown}}

replies.body: Usually they keep their schedule. There's still a few days in October, so I'd just say keep your eyes peeled for the skin sale for the next few days.
